<h3>PALS (Patient advice and liaison service)</h3>
<p><a href="mailto:customerservice@aintree.nhs.uk">customerservice@aintree.nhs.uk</a></p>
<div class="pals-text">
<p>You can talk to PALS who provide confidential advice and support to patients, families and their carers, and can provide information on the NHS and health related matters.</p>
<p>Now known as Patient Advice and Complaints Team.</p>
