<h3>Travel information</h3>
<p>Aintree is well served by public transport systems.<br/>Many bus routes pass the site of Aintree University Hospital. Please check with Merseytravel for up to date schedule information: <a href="http://www.merseytravel.gov.uk">www.merseytravel.gov.uk</a></p><br/><p>Fazakerley railway station is located on the Kirkby - Liverpool Line and is closest to the hospital. It is over the road from the hospital grounds but it is approximately a 15 minute walk to the Main Entrance / Outpatients Area.<br/>Â <br/>Further times/details of public transport to the hospital are available by calling Traveline on 0871 200 22 33.</p>
